title: Everything You Need to Know About Jayde Pierce???Bieber???s Rumored New Girlfriend:
text:
You may have heard about Justin Bieber 's somewhat scandalous trip to Bora Bora with 20-year-old model Jayde Pierce, where he roamed the deck of his luxurious beach-front hut sans clothing. Although Jayde and Justin have not confirmed their relationship, one could guess from their, uh, comfort level that there might be something going on between the two.
Even if our hearts can't bare to see anyone replace Selena Gomez (though the singer insists she's moved on ), it's time we get to know the newest lady in Bieber's life.
First off, she's gorgeous.
